  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access to 1.0 Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/ff2fd556bea6868c2499d87441927fc2.avif?t=1773277574\" width=600 height=1192 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fd2982f044d0f8528d37691a7906d201.apng?t=1773277574\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fd2982f044d0f8528d37691a7906d201.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" class=\"bb_img\" width=734 height=162 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/72547fddf80d18adeb8e113ad49a433e.webp?t=1773277574\" width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm the solo developer of Seeds of Calamity. I've always loved farming sims, and one day I thought, 'What the hell, I could make one too.' So I did! Seeds of Calamity is a peaceful, slow-paced game designed to fit your playstyle. From vibrant pixel-art visuals to a relaxing day-to-day rhythm, it offers a warm and welcoming experience. Whether you're exploring, farming, or helping out your neighbors, every moment is crafted with care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fafbc9c60881efe216af43edb441b42d.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" width=700 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fafbc9c60881efe216af43edb441b42d.webm?t=1773277574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a quiet wayside village you’d pass by in a classic JRPG – you and your fluffy Spellbook Companion tend your farm, help the community, and explore dungeons filled with challenge and treasure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/efd57b2e65a0294fae577815d853f974.webp?t=1773277574\" width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twenty years after the Great Calamity, the land is finally recovering. As a young adventurer, you’ll leave the bustling capital to settle in a quiet village on the frontier. Here, you’ll build a cozy farm, help your neighbors, and uncover the small joys of life in a world healing from its past. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/03da33bfbe4c3056190e3bd215b7aa99.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" width=700 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/03da33bfbe4c3056190e3bd215b7aa99.webm?t=1773277574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/ea28f3e053826dbd8b3b976e76e6ce27.webp?t=1773277574\" width=800 height=62 /></span>Tend crops, raise animals, and craft tools to grow your farm through the seasons! Help rebuild by sending resources to the capital and supporting your community. Celebrate the post-Calamity world with festivals, from harvest feasts to moonlit gatherings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/300e9f0212085fdf79d22d8ac4a38940.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" width=700 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/300e9f0212085fdf79d22d8ac4a38940.webm?t=1773277574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/6e28ca88c7bfe1bea914155af0c2e894.apng?t=1773277574\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/6e28ca88c7bfe1bea914155af0c2e894.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" class=\"bb_img\" width=741 height=64 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond the village, dungeons brimming with monsters, treasures, and artifacts await discovery. With the help of your Spellbook Companion, battle slimes and bosses in accessible, turn-based combat. Gather rare resources to improve your farm and unlock new possibilities for growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/e26dfd213e475377a95ce5c5fa6c4776.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" width=700 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/e26dfd213e475377a95ce5c5fa6c4776.webm?t=1773277574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/8c383cef86a2af4fcf33f35720cb7a81.apng?t=1773277574\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/8c383cef86a2af4fcf33f35720cb7a81.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" class=\"bb_img\" width=742 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Spellbook Companion is your constant ally, guiding you through your journey. This magical friend helps you uncover hidden treasures, catalog recipes and quests, and even casts spells in battle. It’s more than a companion – it’s an essential part of your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/b1f81d8757487fb30537d80111f07267.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" width=700 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/b1f81d8757487fb30537d80111f07267.webm?t=1773277574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/6e2d79db7e0b8184fe78285bc09e2893.webp?t=1773277574\" width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seeds of Calamity is designed with inclusivity in mind, featuring extensive accessibility options. Adjust controls, length of day, colors, difficulty, visuals, and more to ensure the game feels right for you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into a world rebuilding from its past, one crop, friendship, and adventure at a time!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fd2982f044d0f8528d37691a7906d201.apng?t=1773277574\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fd2982f044d0f8528d37691a7906d201.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" class=\"bb_img\" width=734 height=162 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/72547fddf80d18adeb8e113ad49a433e.webp?t=1773277574\" width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm the solo developer of Seeds of Calamity. I've always loved farming sims, and one day I thought, 'What the hell, I could make one too.' So I did! Seeds of Calamity is a peaceful, slow-paced game designed to fit your playstyle. From vibrant pixel-art visuals to a relaxing day-to-day rhythm, it offers a warm and welcoming experience. Whether you're exploring, farming, or helping out your neighbors, every moment is crafted with care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fafbc9c60881efe216af43edb441b42d.poster.avif?t=1773277574\" width=700 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780070/extras/fafbc9c60881efe216af43edb441b42d.webm?t=1773277574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a quiet wayside village you’d pass by in a classic JRPG – you and your fluffy Spellbook Companion tend your farm, help the community, and explore dungeons filled with challenge and treasure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class